greyuser: Len bounceri a vyšší staff môže spustiť bota.
bouncer: Bot nemôže posunúť človeka, keď beží na bouncerovi.
songknown: /me :repeat: Tento song bol hraný pred %%PLAYS%% minútami v poslednej %%TIMETOTAL%%, posledné hranie bolo pred %%LASTTIME%% :repeat:
timelimit: /me @%%NAME%%, tvoj song je dlhší než %%MAXLENGTH%% minút, potrebuješ právo na hranie dlhších songov.
permissionownsong: /me :up: @%%NAME%% má právo hrať jeho vlastné výtvory!
isblacklisted: /me Tento song je v %%BLACKLIST%% blackliste! Skipujem...
isopen: /me Ruleta je spustená! Napíš !join aby si sa zúčastnil!
alreadyadding: /me Užívateľ už bol pridaný! Zmeniť požadovanú polohu na %%POSITION%%.
notdisconnected: /me @%%NAME%% sa neodhlásil kým som tu bol.
noposition: /me Nepoznám poslednú pozíciu. Zoznam čakania sa potrebuje aktualizovať aspoň raz v poslednej pozícii užívateľa.
valid: /me @%%NAME%% sa odhlásil pred %%TIME%% minútami a bol na pozícii %%POSITION%%.
warning1: /me @%%NAME%%, you have been afk for %%TIME%%, please respond within 2 minutes or you will be removed.
warning2: /me @%%NAME%%, you will be removed due to AFK soon if you don't respond.
afkremove: /me @%%NAME%%, you have been removed for being afk for %%TIME%%. You were at position %%POSITION%%. Chat at least once every %%MAXIMUMAFK%% minutes if you want to play a song.
roomadvertising: /me @%%NAME%%, neposielaj linky od druhých roomiek prosím.
adfly: /me @%%NAME%%, prosím zmeň tvoj autowoot program. Preferujeme PlugCubed: http://plugcubed.net/
voteskiplimit: /me [@%%NAME%%] Voteskip limit je nastavený na %%LIMIT%% mehov.
voteskipexceededlimit: /me @%%NAME%%, tvoj song prekročil voteskip limit (%%LIMIT%% mehov).
voteskipinvalidlimit: /me [@%%NAME%%] Neplatný voteskip limit, skúste to prosím znova s použitím čísla, čo znamená počet mehov.
activeusersintime: /me [@%%NAME%% Tam boli %%AMOUNT%% užívateľov chatujúcich posledných %%TIME%% minút.
maximumafktimeset: /me [@%%NAME%%] Maximum afk trvanie nastavené na %%TIME%% minút.
brandambassador: /me Brand Ambassador sú dobrovoľnici pre plug.dj. Podporujú udalosti, pomáhajú komunitám a zdieľajú plug.dj po celom svete. Pre viac informácií: http://blog.plug.dj/brand-ambassadors/
bouncerplusrank: /me [@%%NAME%%] Musíš byť minimálne manager na aktiváciu Bouncer+.
nousercookie: /em nevidím %%NAME%% v roomke, tak som zjedol koláč sám.
selfcookie: /me @%%NAME%%, si trochu chamtivý, nie? Dať si koláč pre seba, bah. Podeľ sa s ostatnými ľuďmi!
cycleguardtime: /me [@%%NAME%%] The cycleguard is set to %%TIME%% minute(s).
dclookuprank: /me [@%%NAME%%] Only bouncers and above can do a lookup for others.
notinwaitlist: /me @%%NAME%%, you are not on the waitlist.
eta: /me @%%NAME%% you will reach the booth in approximately %%TIME%%.
starterhelp: /me This image will get you started on plug: %%LINK%%
roulettejoin: /me @%%NAME%% joined the roulette! (!leave if you regret it.)
jointime: /me [@%%NAMEFROM%%] @%%USERNAME%% has been in the room for %%TIME%%.
kickrank: /me [@%%NAME%%] you can't kick users with an equal or higher rank than you!
kick: /me [@%%NAME%%], @%%USERNAME%% you are being kicked from the community for %%TIME%% minutes.
lockskippos: /me [@%%NAME%%] Lockskip will now move the dj to position %%POSITION%%.
lockguardtime: /me [@%%NAME%%] The lockguard is set to %%TIME%% minute(s).
maxlengthtime: /me [@%%NAME%%] The maximum song duration is set to %%TIME%% minutes.
addbotwaitlist: /me @%%NAME%%, don't try to add me to the waitlist, please.

muterank: /me [@%%NAME%%] You can't mute persons with an equal or higher rank than you.
removenotinwl: /me [@%%NAME%%] Specified user @%%USERNAME%% is not in the waitlist.
roomrules: /me Please find the room rules here: %%LINK%%
sessionstats: /me [@%%NAME%%] Total woots: %%WOOTS%%, total mehs: %%MEHS%%, total grabs: %%GRABS%%.
swapinvalid: /me [@%%NAME%%] Invalid user specified. (No names with spaces!)
swapwlonly: /me [@%%NAME%%] Please only swap users that are in the waitlist!
genres: /me Please find the permissible room genres here: %%LINK%%
